==============================
      NFF Exporter
==============================

Installation:

export_nff directory locations:

Windows 7 - C:\Users\%username%\AppData\Roaming\Blender Foundation\Blender\2.5x\scripts\addons
Windows XP - C:\Documents and Settings\%username%\Application Data\Blender Foundation\Blender\2.6x\scripts\addons
Linux - /home/$user/.config/blender/$version/scripts/addons

In Blender:

File -> User preferences -> Addons 
Pick category (from the left side of the window): Import-Export
Enable: Import-Export: Neutral File Format Exporter

To export:

File -> Export -> Neutral File Format (.nff)
Choose amongst the options from the left end of the window:
  Export Meshes
  Export Normals
  Export Materials
  Export UV Coordinates

